WEBVTT

00:00.760 --> 00:02.159
PREVIOUSLY...

00:02.170 --> 00:04.195
YOU THINK I KILLED LILLY.
CALM DOWN.

00:04.200 --> 00:05.667
WHY?! DO YOU THINK
I'M GONNA KILL YOU, TOO?!

00:05.670 --> 00:08.468
YOU HAVEN'T SEEN DUNCAN
TONIGHT, HAVE YOU?

00:08.470 --> 00:11.735
HE'S MISSING. HIS PARENTS THINK
HE MAY HAVE RUN AWAY.

00:12.480 --> 00:14.334
YOU DIDN'T WANT THEM
DATING, EITHER.

00:14.340 --> 00:16.240
YEAH, I WISH MOM
WOULD HAVE FOUND A GUY

00:16.250 --> 00:17.945
WHO WASN'T
MY BEST FRIEND'S DAD.

00:17.950 --> 00:19.747
I KNOW LILLY LOVED YOU.

00:19.750 --> 00:21.012
NOT LIKE I LOVED HER.

00:21.020 --> 00:23.238
I DON'T HAVE TO
FEEL GUILTY ANYMORE.

00:23.250 --> 00:25.343
FEEL GUILTY ABOUT WHAT?

00:25.350 --> 00:28.148
WHAT ARE WE DOING?

00:28.160 --> 00:31.049
NO IDEA.

00:31.060 --> 00:32.698
COME ON!

00:32.700 --> 00:34.497
[ HORNS HONKING ]

00:37.730 --> 00:40.335
[ HONKING CONTINUES ]

00:50.250 --> 00:51.899
[ HONKING CONTINUES ]

00:51.910 --> 00:53.411
UH-OH.

00:53.420 --> 00:54.819
SOMEONE'S GOT HER EYE ON
THAT "MISS WHITE TRASH" TITLE.

00:54.820 --> 00:56.583
SOLID EFFORT
IN THE TALENT COMPETITION,

00:56.590 --> 00:59.286
BUT I'D LIKE TO SEE
THAT CAR ON CINDER BLOCKS.

00:59.290 --> 01:00.814
GUYS, COME ON, HUH?

01:00.820 --> 01:02.253
I KNOW. GUYS, COME ON.

01:02.260 --> 01:04.979
THE TALENT IS MAKING
A GRILLED-CHEESE SANDWICH

01:04.990 --> 01:06.150
ON THE ENGINE BLOCK.

01:06.160 --> 01:07.696
GUYS, COME ON.

01:07.700 --> 01:10.328
YOU CAN'T PUT YOUR CAR
UP ON BLOCKS IN THE YARD

01:10.330 --> 01:11.922
IF YOU DON'T HAVE A YARD.

01:11.930 --> 01:15.229
I THINK I CAN DO BOTH SIDES
OF THIS LI'I'I'LE ACT NOW.

01:18.810 --> 01:20.937
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

01:20.940 --> 01:24.205
SO NEXT TIME, DON'T BOTHER.
I GOT IT COVERED.

01:33.620 --> 01:35.156
SO, THAT'S IT?

01:35.160 --> 01:36.582
I MEAN, JUST LIKE THAT,

01:36.590 --> 01:40.219
YOU FLUSH A TWO-YEAR
RELATIONSHIP DOWN THE TOILET?

01:40.230 --> 01:42.619
NO, TAD.

01:42.630 --> 01:43.892
IT'S...

01:43.900 --> 01:46.835
WE'VE BEEN GOING OUT
SINCE I WAS A FRESHMAN,

01:46.840 --> 01:48.239
AND I JUST FEEL LIKE --

01:48.240 --> 01:49.867
WHAT DID I DO WRONG?
NOTHING.
IT'S JUST...

01:49.870 --> 01:52.304
YOU'RE GRADUATING
IN A MONTH, AND --

01:52.310 --> 01:55.700
AND WHAT? YOU DON'T TRUST ME?
WITH COLLEGE AND ALL THAT?

01:55.710 --> 01:59.168
TAD, I CAN'T IMAGINE DOING
THE WHOLE LONG-DISTANCE THING.

01:59.180 --> 02:00.670
BUT IT'S ONLY
FOR A YEAR.

02:00.680 --> 02:02.682
NO, IT'S FOUR YEARS
AT THE ACADEMY,

02:02.690 --> 02:06.285
AND THEN FOUR YEARS OF THE NAW,
AND THEN -- I DON'T KNOW.

02:07.790 --> 02:12.159
LOOK -- LOOK,
JUST LISTEN TO THIS, PLEASE.

02:12.160 --> 02:13.491
I DON'T WANT ANOTHER MIX.

02:13.500 --> 02:15.798
IT'S SOMETHING I WROTE FOR YOU
ON MY GUITAR.

02:15.800 --> 02:18.928
LOOK, A SONG ISN'T GONNA
MAKE IT BETTER, TAD.

02:18.930 --> 02:20.397
IT'S OVER.

02:22.640 --> 02:25.803
BEFORE YOU GO, THERE'S
SOMETHING YOU SHOULD SEE.

02:25.810 --> 02:28.335
YOU'RE NOT GONNA
CHANGE MY MIND.

02:30.510 --> 02:34.310
[ CARMEN GIGGLING ]

02:37.290 --> 02:40.612
[ Crying ] I DON'T EVEN
REMEMBER DOING IT.

02:42.830 --> 02:44.127
I MUST HAVE BEEN WASTED.

02:44.130 --> 02:46.451
I WOULD NEVER
DO SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

02:46.460 --> 02:48.189
IT'S TOTALLY DISGUSTING.

02:48.200 --> 02:52.534
YOU MEAN...
YOU TWO HAVING SEX?

02:52.540 --> 02:54.235
WORSE.

02:54.240 --> 02:58.665
I'M SKINNY-DIPPING
IN SOME HOT TUB AND...

02:58.670 --> 03:02.379
I HAVE THIS...POPSICLE
IN MY...

03:02.380 --> 03:04.871
DO YOU THINK
HE'S SERIOUS?

03:04.880 --> 03:06.313
I DON'T KNOW.

03:06.320 --> 03:08.413
WHEN I SAID I WANTED
TO BREAK UP, HE WAS...

03:08.420 --> 03:09.842
I CAN'T TAKE THE CHANCE.

03:09.850 --> 03:12.182
I NEED YOU TO GET ME
THAT PHONE, VERONICA.

03:12.190 --> 03:14.158
YOU CAN DO THAT,
CAN'T YOU?

03:14.160 --> 03:17.550
OH, YEAH.
BANK ON IT.

03:17.560 --> 03:21.553
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

03:21.560 --> 03:27.260
* BUT I HAVEN'T THOUGHT OF YOU
LATELY AT ALL *

03:27.700 --> 03:30.009
* COME ON, NOW, SUGAR *

03:30.010 --> 03:32.934
* BRING IT ON, BRING IT ON,
YEAH *

03:32.940 --> 03:35.431
* JUST REMEMBER ME WHEN *

03:35.440 --> 03:40.616
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS
A LONG TIME AGO *

03:40.620 --> 03:43.509
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

04:03.640 --> 04:06.234
WHAT?
I BLOCKADED THE DOOR.

04:06.240 --> 04:08.435
I HUNG
AN "OUT OF ORDER" SIGN.

04:08.440 --> 04:10.271
THIS IS WRONG.

04:10.280 --> 04:13.272
I MEAN, A BOY
IN A GIRLS' BATHROOM IS JUST --

04:13.280 --> 04:15.578
SO WRONG, IT'S RIGHT?
YES.

04:17.020 --> 04:19.488
[ SIGHS ] I'M SORRY
ABOUT DICK AND THOSE GUYS.

04:19.490 --> 04:21.879
DICK AND THOSE GUYS
DON'T BOTHER ME.

04:21.890 --> 04:24.484
BESIDES, YOU AND I
HAVE TO KEEP UP APPEARANCES

04:24.490 --> 04:26.993
BECAUSE DUNCAN IS GONNA
COME HOME SOMEDAY.

04:27.000 --> 04:30.959
AND I DON'T WANT HIM
TO HEAR ABOUT US -- THIS --

04:30.970 --> 04:33.029
FROM SOMEONE ELSE.

04:34.440 --> 04:37.932
[ SIGHS ] I'M BEYOND TARDY
FOR MY PHYSICS CLASS.

04:37.940 --> 04:42.639
IF I REMEMBER RIGHT,
TIME TRAVEL IS NOT YET POSSIBLE.

04:42.650 --> 04:44.845
SO TRY PETI'Y CORRUPTION.

04:44.850 --> 04:46.078
HMM?

04:46.080 --> 04:50.380
TARDY EXCUSE SLIPS,
DATE-STAMPED, UNTRACEABLE.

04:52.020 --> 04:54.488
I KNOW PEOPLE.

04:56.260 --> 04:57.989
IT'S CLEAR.

04:57.990 --> 04:59.958
GOOD LUCK IN PHYSICS.

04:59.960 --> 05:01.097
REMEMBER...

05:01.100 --> 05:02.397
[ BOTH GIGGLE ]

05:02.400 --> 05:04.891
FORCE EQUALS
MASS TIMES ACCELERATION.

05:04.900 --> 05:06.265
MMM.

05:06.270 --> 05:09.933
LIGHT IS A PARTICLE THAT CAN
EXHIBIT PROPERTIES OF A WAVE.

05:09.940 --> 05:13.501
I COULD LEARN MORE
STAYING HERE WITH YOU.

05:13.510 --> 05:16.377
I HAVE THINGS TO DO.

05:20.150 --> 05:22.414
Veronica: LIKE COOL DOWN.

05:22.420 --> 05:23.819
[ SIGHS ]

05:23.820 --> 05:26.857
I MADE A PROMISE TO CARMEN.

05:26.860 --> 05:29.317
THANK GOD
FOR DISPOSABLE CELLPHONES.

05:29.320 --> 05:31.788
NO OFFENSE,
BUT YOU LOOK...ODD.

05:31.790 --> 05:35.157
I JUST WATCHED OUR PARENTS
CUDDLE ON THE COUCH LAST NIGHT.

05:35.160 --> 05:36.923
MY EYES -- THEY BURN.

05:36.930 --> 05:39.569
ANY IDEA WHAT OUR PARENTS DO
MONDAYS AND WEDNESDAYS

05:39.570 --> 05:42.164
FROM 6:00 TO 10:00
THAT REQUIRES AN OVERNIGHT BAG?

05:42.170 --> 05:44.832
AS FAR AS I'M CONCERNED,
THEY PLAY BINGO AT THE V.F.W.

05:44.840 --> 05:46.728
THAT'S MY STORY.
I'M STICKING WITH IT.

05:46.740 --> 05:49.038
THE BEST WAY
TO DEAL WITH THINGS LIKE THIS --

05:49.040 --> 05:50.348
PRETEND THEY DON'T EXIST.

05:50.350 --> 05:52.648
YOU MIND CALLING THIS NUMBER
SIXTH PERIOD?

05:52.650 --> 05:54.072
SURE, ALL RIGHT.

05:54.080 --> 05:56.389
THEY DON'T EXIST?
DEAL.

05:57.550 --> 06:00.587
YOU MIND HELPING ME
WITH A BUMP-AND-BAIT HERE?

06:00.590 --> 06:04.219
SO I WAS ALL, "NO WAY."
AND HE WAS LIKE, "YEAH, WAY."

06:04.230 --> 06:05.720
[ GASPS ] I'M SO SORRY.

06:05.730 --> 06:09.052
WATCH WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

06:09.060 --> 06:11.665
OKELY DOKELY.

06:11.670 --> 06:13.467
HE DID NOT SAY THAT.

06:13.470 --> 06:14.835
UNH-UNH.

06:14.840 --> 06:15.738
UNH-UNH!

06:15.740 --> 06:17.469
[GASPS] UNH-UNH!!

06:17.470 --> 06:21.577
EXCUSE ME. WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING?

06:21.580 --> 06:22.899
OKAY, CIAO FOR NOW.

06:22.910 --> 06:25.549
THIS IS, LIKE,
STUDY HALL, RIGHT?

06:26.420 --> 06:31.744
I WAS EXCUSED FROM GYM CLASS
FOR, UM...PERSONAL REASONS.

06:31.750 --> 06:36.016
ARE YOU NOT FAMILIAR WITH
THIS SCHOOL'S CELLPHONE POLICY?

06:39.630 --> 06:43.361
YOU CAN PICK THIS UP
AFTER SCHOOL.

06:43.370 --> 06:45.691
Man: WE CALL IT "SYMBIOSIS."

06:45.700 --> 06:48.498
THAT LITERALLY MEANS
"LIVING TOGETHER."

06:48.500 --> 06:51.765
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

06:51.770 --> 06:55.206
TAD, I BELIEVE
YOUR BAG IS RINGING.

06:55.210 --> 06:57.747
[ RINGING CONTINUES ]

07:05.150 --> 07:07.050
GIVE ME A BREAK.
IT'S NOT EVEN ON.

07:07.060 --> 07:09.051
I KNOW YOU KNOW THE POLICY,
MR. WILSON,

07:09.060 --> 07:11.381
BECAUSE YOU JUST SAW
A DEMONSTRATION.

07:11.390 --> 07:14.052
I'M AN EQUAL-OPPORTUNITY
CON FISCATOR.

07:28.010 --> 07:29.602
MS. DUNN.

07:30.180 --> 07:32.205
I VOLUNTEERED
TO SEPARATE THE RECYCLING

07:32.210 --> 07:34.474
FROM THE CAFETERIA TRASH
THIS AFTERNOON.

07:34.480 --> 07:37.278
CAN I BE EXCUSED
FROM CLASS EARLY?

07:37.290 --> 07:39.656
[ SCHOOL BELL RINGS ]

07:43.090 --> 07:45.581
HI. I'M HERE
TO GET MY PHONE BACK.

07:45.590 --> 07:46.750
CONSIDER THIS A WARNING.

07:46.760 --> 07:48.296
NEXT TIME,
I'M KEEPING IT,

07:48.300 --> 07:51.098
AND YOU'LL HAVE TO GOSSIP
WITH TWO CANS AND A STRING.

07:51.100 --> 07:54.160
I'M NOT SURE WHAT THAT MEANS,
BUT I'M TOTALLY WARNED.

07:54.170 --> 07:56.161
I SWEAR.

07:59.580 --> 08:01.707
UH, YUP.

08:05.310 --> 08:07.175
WAIT, THIS ISN'T MINE.

08:11.050 --> 08:13.587
VERONICA MARS.

08:15.290 --> 08:17.451
HEY, HONEY.

08:17.460 --> 08:18.927
HOW'S SCHOOL?

08:18.930 --> 08:21.899
YOU KNOW -- MEAN KIDS,
INDIFFERENT TEACHERS,

08:21.900 --> 08:24.164
CRUMBLING INFRASTRUCTURE.

08:24.170 --> 08:25.819
SO, WHY ARE YOU SMILING?

08:25.830 --> 08:28.139
BECAUSE
I'M SAVORING THE IRONY.

08:28.140 --> 08:31.337
IMAGINE THE MARS FAMILY
SENDING OUR HEIR, VERONICA,

08:31.340 --> 08:32.830
TO AN IW-LEAGUE COLLEGE

08:32.840 --> 08:35.172
WITH MONEY FROM THE BOUNTY
ON THE KANE HEIR.

08:35.180 --> 08:38.172
FOR INFORMATION ON THE
WHEREABOUTS OF DUNCAN KANE...

08:38.180 --> 08:40.011
50 GRAND?!

08:40.020 --> 08:41.339
NOT BAD.

08:41.350 --> 08:42.681
MONEY FOR NOTHING.

08:42.690 --> 08:44.646
THAT'S YOUR FIRST TWO YEARS
RIGHT THERE.

08:44.650 --> 08:47.778
IT MIGHT NOT BE
AS EASY AS YOU THINK.

08:47.790 --> 08:49.348
COME ON, HONEY.
DUNCAN KANE?

08:49.360 --> 08:51.658
A SHELTERED RICH KID WHO HAS
MAIDS FOLD HIS UNDERWEAR?

08:51.660 --> 08:53.457
I THINK I'LL BE ABLE
TO TRACK HIM DOWN.

08:53.460 --> 08:57.294
I'M ONLY WORRIED
ABOUT BEATING THE OTHER PROS.

08:57.300 --> 09:00.963
YEAH, HE'S A BIG FISH
IN A VERY SMALL BARREL.

09:02.670 --> 09:03.898
WHAT IS IT?

09:03.910 --> 09:05.468
YOU KNOW
THAT ENTERTAINMENT LAWYER

09:05.470 --> 09:07.404
YOU'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR
ALL YEAR?

09:07.410 --> 09:08.308
YEAH?

09:08.310 --> 09:09.607
I WAS TELLING MEG

09:09.610 --> 09:11.771
ABOUT HOW HARD
THE GUY HAS BEEN TO FIND

09:11.780 --> 09:14.248
AND ALL THE TRICKS
YOU USE TO DISAPPEAR.

09:14.250 --> 09:17.947
AND DUNCAN WAS SITTING
RIGHT THERE LISTENING.

09:17.950 --> 09:20.214
BUT, LOOKING ON
THE BRIGHT SIDE,

09:20.220 --> 09:23.929
ALL THOSE OTHER PROFESSIONALS
WON'T FIND HIM FIRST.

09:23.930 --> 09:26.182
WHAT DID YOU TELL HIM?

09:26.190 --> 09:29.159
USE CASH.
DON'T USE A CREDIT CARD.

09:29.160 --> 09:31.162
DON'T USE YOUR OWN CAR.

09:31.170 --> 09:32.398
THE BASICS.

09:32.400 --> 09:36.564
I MIGHT HAVE MENTIONED
RECYCLING PASSPORTS ON eBAY.

09:38.710 --> 09:42.077
BUT WITH YOUR EXPERTISE
AND MY CAN-DO SPIRIT,

09:42.080 --> 09:44.241
WE CAN DO IT --
FAMILY PROJECT.

09:44.250 --> 09:46.844
I HAVE A FRIEND
WHO CAN PLAY THE eBAY ANGLE,

09:46.850 --> 09:48.249
MIGHT BE ABLE TO --

09:48.250 --> 09:51.481
[ HUMMING ]

09:51.490 --> 09:53.310
HELLO, MR. MARS.

09:53.320 --> 09:54.685
HEY, VERONICA.

09:54.690 --> 09:56.157
HOW'S SCHOOL?

09:56.160 --> 09:57.650
HI, MS. FENNEL.

09:57.660 --> 09:59.719
IT'S FINE.

10:01.230 --> 10:05.189
WE'LL BE BACK
AROUND 8:00 OR SO.

10:05.200 --> 10:06.599
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

10:06.600 --> 10:08.033
OUT.

10:08.040 --> 10:12.158
WHY DON'T YOU GET STARTED
ON THAT PASSPORT THING.

10:15.740 --> 10:17.799
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

10:17.810 --> 10:19.573
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

10:19.580 --> 10:23.710
SO...DID IT WORK?

10:23.720 --> 10:25.039
SUCCESS.

10:25.050 --> 10:28.281
OH, THANK YOU,
THANK YOU, THANK YOU.

10:29.460 --> 10:31.382
YOU DIDN'T WATCH IT,
DID YOU?

10:33.560 --> 10:36.097
YOU SAVED MY LIFE,
VERONICA.

10:36.100 --> 10:38.819
LOOK, CARMEN,
JUST BECAUSE WE GOT THE PHONE

10:38.830 --> 10:40.388
DOESN'T MEAN
THE VIDEO'S DEAD.

10:40.400 --> 10:43.938
YOU GOT TO KNOW IT'S IMPOSSIBLE
TO DESTROY A DIGITAL FILE

10:43.940 --> 10:45.430
WITH ANY KIND
OF CERTAINTY.

10:45.440 --> 10:49.001
TAD ISN'T REALLY
A THINK-AHEAD KIND OF GUY.

10:56.720 --> 10:58.642
THAT FELT GOOD.

10:58.650 --> 11:01.813
JUSTICE IS SERVED.

11:03.030 --> 11:05.658
INSTANT MESSAGE
FROM "TOP GUN."

11:05.660 --> 11:08.697
THAT'S TAD.

11:13.770 --> 11:16.295
MMM. MMM --

11:18.870 --> 11:21.009
OH, MY GOD.

11:25.050 --> 11:26.779
SO, THE THING IS FIGURING OUT
IF ANY PASSPORTS WERE SOLD

11:26.780 --> 11:28.247
ON ANY
OF THESE AUCTION SITES

11:28.250 --> 11:30.639
AND SHIPPED
ANYWHERE NEAR NEPTUNE.

11:30.650 --> 11:32.140
MAN, VERONICA.

11:32.150 --> 11:34.687
HAVE YOU EVER ASKED FOR HELP
WITH ANYTHING NORMAL?

11:34.690 --> 11:36.055
WHAT FUN WOULD THAT BE?

11:36.060 --> 11:38.620
ALL RIGHT.
WELL, I'LL GET BACK TO YOU.

11:38.630 --> 11:40.928
THANKS A ZILLION, MAC.

11:42.660 --> 11:46.027
Veronica: SO, CARMEN'S BACK
WITH TAD -- IT'S EITHER THAT,

11:46.030 --> 11:48.396
OR HE SENDS THE VIDEO
TO THE WHOLE SCHOOL.

11:48.400 --> 11:51.039
NOW, THAT'S A SHAME --
NEIGHBORHOOD GIRL LIKE THAT

11:51.040 --> 11:52.598
WASTING HER ASSETS
ON A WHITE BOY.

11:52.610 --> 11:55.773
ISN'T THAT THAT CHICK YOU HAD
A CRUSH ON IN EIGHTH GRADE?

11:55.780 --> 11:57.771
TOO BAD YOU AIN'T RICH...
AND WHITE,

11:57.780 --> 11:59.771
'CAUSE DAMN,
DID SHE GROW UP NICE!

11:59.780 --> 12:02.271
"GET MAROONED."

12:02.280 --> 12:04.840
GREAT. ANOTHER ISLAND-CENTRIC
PROM THEME.

12:04.850 --> 12:07.011
ANOTHER YEAR
OF DOUBLE-DIGIT I.Q. JOCKS

12:07.020 --> 12:09.386
LAUGHING AT THEIR OWN JOKES
ABOUT GETTING "LEId"

12:09.390 --> 12:11.585
AS FRESHMAN GIRLS
PUT FLOWERS AROUND THEIR NECKS.

12:11.590 --> 12:14.559
I DON'T SEE ANYBODY FORCING YOU
TO BUY TICKETS, QUEER-BAIT.

12:14.560 --> 12:17.723
I'M SORRY. AM I GIVING AWAY
YOUR BEST MATERIAL?

12:17.730 --> 12:19.834
ISN'T THE GAY PROM
NEXT FRIDAY

12:19.840 --> 12:21.865
IN THE DOG BEACH
MEN'S ROOM?

12:21.870 --> 12:23.929
SO I GUESS
I'LL SEE YOU THERE, SAILOR.

12:23.940 --> 12:27.899
YO, WHAT DID YOU
JUST SAY TO ME, BOY GEORGE?

12:27.910 --> 12:29.707
COME ON. THE NAW?

12:29.710 --> 12:31.302
COVER MY BACK, WINGMAN.

12:31.310 --> 12:34.074
THE REAR ADMIRAL WANTS US TO
POUND AWAY WITH THE 10-INCH GUN.

12:34.080 --> 12:36.071
ISN'T JUST
JOINING THE NAW ALONE

12:36.080 --> 12:38.844
GAY ENOUGH TO GET YOU
THROWN OUT OF THE NAW?

12:38.850 --> 12:41.250
[ LAUGHTER ]

12:41.260 --> 12:45.321
THE PROM IS SUPPOSED TO BE
FOR TRADITIONAL COUPLES, MAN.

12:45.330 --> 12:48.458
WHAT'S MORE TRADITIONAL
THAN FAIRIES AND FAT CHICKS?

12:48.460 --> 12:51.463
[ LAUGHTER ]

12:53.100 --> 12:55.330
WHY WOULD CARMEN
WANT TO DUMP SUCH A CHARMER?

12:55.340 --> 12:59.106
ONE DAY, AND I ALREADY FEEL LIKE
I NEED A LONG, HOT SHOWER.

12:59.110 --> 13:01.931
I DON'T KNOW HOW LONG
I CAN KEEP THIS UP.

13:01.940 --> 13:04.147
WHAT YOU NEED
IS AN EXIT STRATEGY.

13:04.150 --> 13:06.539
YOU KNOW WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN,
VERONICA?

13:06.550 --> 13:09.917
I'M GONNA END UP
A DOWNLOADABLE NATIONAL JOKE.

13:09.920 --> 13:12.684
YOU KNOW, RIGHT UP THERE
WITH PARIS HILTON

13:12.690 --> 13:14.317
OR THAT "STAR WARS" KID.

13:14.320 --> 13:17.027
I'LL BE THE VIDEO THAT EVERYONE
E-MAILS THEIR FRIENDS.

13:17.030 --> 13:19.089
JUST GOOGLE
"POPSICLE GIRL,"

13:19.090 --> 13:23.026
AND THERE I'LL BE
FOR THE REST OF HUMAN HISTORY.

13:23.030 --> 13:25.021
AND I CAN'T STOP HIM.

13:25.030 --> 13:29.364
UNLESS YOU HAD SOMETHING
THAT WOULD RUIN TAD BACK.

13:29.370 --> 13:31.361
YOU KNOW?
GET YOUR OWN A-BOMB.

13:31.370 --> 13:34.237
IT PREVENTS HIM
FROM LAUNCHING A FIRST STRIKE --

13:34.240 --> 13:36.128
MUTUALLY ASSURED
DESTRUCTION.

13:36.140 --> 13:38.142
YOU'RE NOT GONNA
FIND ANY DIRT ON TAD,

13:38.150 --> 13:39.640
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU MEAN.

13:39.650 --> 13:43.746
BEYOND HIS PENCHANT FOR
AMATEUR UNDERAGE PORNOGRAPHY?

13:43.750 --> 13:45.012
LEAVE THAT TO ME.

13:45.020 --> 13:46.487
I JUST NEED TO KNOW

13:46.490 --> 13:50.256
THAT YOU'RE WILLING TO GET
YOUR HANDS A LITTLE DIRTY.

13:50.260 --> 13:52.285
IF IT MAKES YOU
FEEL ANY BETTER,

13:55.060 --> 13:56.550
TAD USED TO BE
DIFFERENT.

13:56.560 --> 13:59.324
I MEAN, HE WAS
THE FIRST BOYFRIEND I EVER HAD.

13:59.330 --> 14:01.560
HE WAS THE FIRST GUY
I EVER SLEPT WITH.

14:01.570 --> 14:05.199
THE FIRST GUY WHO GOT YOU DRUNK
AND TOOK DIRTY PICTURES OF YOU?

14:05.970 --> 14:08.234
YOU STILL WANT
TO DATE HIM?

14:08.240 --> 14:10.970
THEN LET'S GET THIS
OVER WITH.

14:10.980 --> 14:12.277
WHAT DO I DO?

14:12.280 --> 14:14.976
YOU INVITE TAD
FOR A ROMANTIC AFTERNOON

14:14.980 --> 14:16.845
ON THE NEPTUNE BOARDWALK.

14:25.060 --> 14:27.858
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?
YOU MISS ME?

14:27.860 --> 14:29.225
ALTERNATOR TROUBLE.

14:29.230 --> 14:32.267
DO YOU THINK YOUR UNCLE
CAN RETURN THE LeBARON

14:32.270 --> 14:34.135
TO ALL ITS ORIGINAL GLORY?

14:34.140 --> 14:36.631
HE COULD GET IT READY
FOR DAYTONA

14:36.640 --> 14:37.902
IF YOU PAY HIM ENOUGH.

14:37.910 --> 14:39.639
THAT WON'T BE NECESSARY.

14:39.640 --> 14:41.176
COME HERE.

14:41.180 --> 14:43.171
THE WORD IS,
THE KANES ARE OFFERING

14:43.180 --> 14:45.205
A NICE LITTLE REWARD
TO FIND DUNCAN.

14:45.210 --> 14:49.271
YOU PICK UP SOME LEADS WHEN
YOU BROKE INTO THE KANE HOUSE?

14:49.280 --> 14:52.545
OR WERE YOU JUST
COVERING YOUR TRACKS?

14:52.550 --> 14:54.188
YOU USED ME.

14:54.190 --> 14:57.125
WELL, WE'RE ALWAYS OWING
EACH OTHER FAVORS, AREN'T WE?

14:57.130 --> 14:58.483
DON'T GIVE ME THAT LOOK.

14:58.490 --> 15:00.492
IF YOU THOUGHT
I'D HURT LILLY,

15:00.500 --> 15:03.298
YOU'D HAVE A HOMING DEVICE
ON MY ASS ALREADY.

15:03.300 --> 15:06.997
I JUST HEARD SOMETHING
I THOUGHT MIGHT BE WORTH, SAY...

15:07.000 --> 15:08.797
10% OF YOUR FINDER'S FEE?

15:08.800 --> 15:10.028
10%?

15:10.040 --> 15:12.133
IT DEPENDS ON
WHAT THAT SOMETHING IS.

15:12.140 --> 15:14.233
HOW ABOUT A CERTAIN
SPOILED WHITE BOY

15:14.240 --> 15:16.037
BOUGHT
A CRAPPED-OUT IMPALA

15:16.040 --> 15:18.247
FROM MY UNCLE'S FRIEND
A FEW WEEKS BACK?

15:18.250 --> 15:20.343
8% -- IF IT PANS OUT.

15:20.350 --> 15:22.818
AND YOU THROW IN
THAT ALTERNATOR.

15:22.820 --> 15:24.447
ALL RIGHT.

15:24.450 --> 15:26.953
HEY, DAD.
YOU GOT A PEN?

15:26.960 --> 15:29.155
A '69 IMPALA.

15:29.160 --> 15:35.395
CALIFORNIA LICENSE PLATE
6GUC788.

15:35.400 --> 15:38.961
AND HE BOUGHT IT FOR $800 CASH
A COUPLE WEEKS AGO.

15:38.970 --> 15:40.437
RIGHT.

15:40.440 --> 15:41.395
BYE.

15:41.400 --> 15:44.233
IT'S ALWAYS BUSINESS
WITH YOU.

15:50.010 --> 15:52.740
SO, THE PLACE IS OURS.

15:52.750 --> 15:54.377
DAD'S AT CLASS.

15:54.380 --> 15:57.213
TRINA'S AT AN EXTREMELY
IMPORTANT PURSE-STORE OPENING

15:57.220 --> 15:58.380
IN BEVERLY HILLS.

15:58.390 --> 16:00.278
YOUR DAD
IS TAKING CLASSES?

16:00.290 --> 16:02.986
EXPLORING THE WORLD
OUTSIDE HIMSELF,

16:02.990 --> 16:05.254
ALL PART OF
THE NEW AARON ECHOLLS.

16:05.260 --> 16:07.524
SPANISH, CERAMICS,
TAE KWON DO,

16:07.530 --> 16:10.988
AND TODAY, GLASSBLOWING
WITH SILVIO PIRELLI,

16:11.000 --> 16:13.992
MASTER OF
OLD-WORLD CRYSTAL.

16:14.000 --> 16:15.137
NICE, HUH?

16:15.140 --> 16:17.005
JUST TWO LESSONS.

16:17.010 --> 16:19.001
AND HE MADE A BONG?

16:19.010 --> 16:20.739
AN URN FOR MY MOM.

16:20.740 --> 16:24.244
YOU KNOW, SINCE THERE WAS
NO BODY AND THUS NO ASHES,

16:24.250 --> 16:26.172
HE FILLED IT
WITH SEAWATER.

16:26.180 --> 16:30.048
BECAUSE SHE JUMPED
INTO THE OCEAN. GET IT?

16:30.050 --> 16:33.759
AT LEAST IT GETS HIM
OUT OF THE HOUSE.

16:33.760 --> 16:35.614
[ LAUGHS ]

16:38.690 --> 16:39.725
HEY.

16:39.730 --> 16:42.858
DO YOU THINK THIS THING...

16:42.860 --> 16:46.193
WILL EVER GET MORE NORMAL?

16:46.200 --> 16:49.169
WHAT, LIKE,
WILL WE EVER HANG AT THE MALL

16:49.170 --> 16:52.139
AND HOLD HANDS
AND BUY EACH OTHER TEDDY BEARS

16:52.140 --> 16:55.029
WITH HEARTS THAT SAY
"I WUV YOU BEARY MUCH"?

16:55.040 --> 16:56.132
YES, EXACTLY THAT.

16:56.140 --> 16:57.573
EXCEPT I WANT MY BEAR WON

16:57.580 --> 16:59.969
THROUGH SOME SORT
OF DEMONSTRATION

16:59.980 --> 17:01.709
OF RING-TOSSING ABILITY.

17:01.720 --> 17:05.588
WELL, SECRETS ARE
KIND OF HOT, TOO.

17:10.230 --> 17:12.790
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

17:12.790 --> 17:15.350
OH, I'M SORRY.

17:15.360 --> 17:19.467
WELL, I DIDN'T REALIZE
YOU HAD COMPANY.

17:20.800 --> 17:22.062
HELLO, VERONICA.

17:24.140 --> 17:25.801
I THOUGHT YOU WERE OUT.

17:25.810 --> 17:28.779
YEAH, WELL, SILVIO CANCELED,
SO I GRABBED SOME SWORDFISH.

17:28.780 --> 17:31.704
I THOUGHT I'D TRY
THAT LIME-TEQUILA MARINADE.

17:31.710 --> 17:37.046
YOU KNOW, I THINK I'LL GET OUT
OF YOU GUYS' HAIR.

17:37.050 --> 17:39.109
THERE'S CHIPS
IF YOU'RE HUNGRY.

17:39.120 --> 17:41.759
THE BLUE CORN --
REALLY GOOD.

17:43.230 --> 17:44.754
OH, MY GOD.

17:44.760 --> 17:48.150
DID I JUST GET CAUGHT BY MY DAD
MAKING OUT ON THE COUCH?

17:48.160 --> 17:50.162
YEAH, YOU GOT
CAUGHT BY YOUR DAD.

17:50.170 --> 17:51.819
I GOT CAUGHT

17:51.830 --> 17:55.061
BY THE STAR OF "BREAKING POINT"
AND "BEYOND THE BREAKING POINT."

17:55.070 --> 17:56.492
THAT'S WEIRD. HMM.

17:56.500 --> 17:59.469
AND I HAVE LIPSTICK
ON MY TEETH.

18:02.680 --> 18:04.079
[ SIGHS ]

18:05.350 --> 18:08.410
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

18:10.190 --> 18:12.181
LOGAN.
LOOK WHO SHOWED UP.

18:12.190 --> 18:14.181
DICK AND, UM...
[ SNAPS FINGERS ]

18:14.190 --> 18:15.748
BEAVER.

18:15.760 --> 18:16.988
BEAV.

18:16.990 --> 18:18.526
THIS IS WHY
YOU COULDN'T SURF?

18:18.530 --> 18:21.124
YOU HAD SOMETHING TO DO
ON THE COUCH?

18:22.130 --> 18:24.997
SORRY, DUDE.
I JUST --

18:25.000 --> 18:26.661
DUDE.

18:27.400 --> 18:29.265
YOU GOT A CHICK HERE?

18:29.270 --> 18:31.158
NO, THAT'S TRINA'S.

18:31.170 --> 18:32.660
SHE'S WITHOUT
HER LIP GLOSS.

18:32.670 --> 18:35.207
IT'S POSSIBLE
SHE'S SUFFERING OUT THERE.

18:35.210 --> 18:36.632
OH, RIGHT.

18:36.640 --> 18:39.473
AND, UH, I'M SUPPOSED
TO TAKE THAT TO HER.

18:43.790 --> 18:45.519
YEAH.

18:46.350 --> 18:48.284
ACTUALLY,
I WAS GONNA GO WITH YOU.

18:48.290 --> 18:51.259
DUDE, NO WAY. YOU ALREADY
BLEW US OFF ON THE WATER.

18:51.260 --> 18:53.694
WE GOT BUSINESS
TO DISCUSS.

18:53.700 --> 18:57.158
THIS WEEKEND, MEXICO --
ANNUAL SURF AND CHICK FEST.

18:57.170 --> 18:58.797
BEAV TALKED
TO THESE CHEERLEADERS.

18:58.800 --> 19:01.496
IT TURNS OUT THEY HAVE
A RETREAT OUTSIDE ROSARITO.

19:01.500 --> 19:04.264
AND THEY JUST GOT SECOND
IN THIS REGIONAL CONTEST.

19:04.270 --> 19:05.760
BEERS, WAVES,

19:05.770 --> 19:08.807
AND WEAK-WILLED CHEERLEADERS
RIGHT NEXT DOOR.

19:08.810 --> 19:10.448
SWEET.

19:10.450 --> 19:14.978
IT LOOKS LIKE LOGAN'S
GONNA BE STUCK FOR A WHILE.

19:14.980 --> 19:16.538
RIDE HOME?

19:18.990 --> 19:23.484
* ME AND YOU
AND A DOG NAMED BOO *

19:23.490 --> 19:26.288
SO, HOW ARE YOU,
VERONICA?

19:26.290 --> 19:27.723
EMBARRASSED.

19:27.730 --> 19:30.392
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]
UNCOMFORTABLE.

19:30.400 --> 19:33.699
OH, DON'T BE.
I WAS A TEENAGER ONCE.

19:33.700 --> 19:37.966
THE THING
I REALLY WANT TO ASK...

19:37.970 --> 19:39.198
HOW'S LOGAN?

19:39.210 --> 19:43.203
I THINK HE'S...

19:43.210 --> 19:44.973
COMING TO TERMS.

19:44.980 --> 19:47.517
HE WAS SUCH A GOOD KID.

19:47.520 --> 19:50.216
WHEN LILLY DIED,
HE BECAME...

19:50.220 --> 19:51.482
DIFFICULT?

19:51.490 --> 19:54.254
[ CHUCKLES ] WELL...

19:54.260 --> 19:57.479
MAYBE IT'S IN THE GENES.

19:57.490 --> 20:01.324
I CAN BE DIFFICULT
FROM TIME TO TIME.

20:01.330 --> 20:03.525
WHATEVER.

20:03.530 --> 20:05.896
I DON'T KNOW
IF YOU GUYS ARE SERIOUS...

20:05.900 --> 20:08.095
OR CASUAL...

20:08.100 --> 20:10.534
OR...JUST TALKING.

20:10.540 --> 20:13.634
BUT YOUR SECRET'S SAFE
WITH ME, HUH?

20:15.480 --> 20:17.004
LOOK, I JUST APPRECIATE

20:17.010 --> 20:19.240
WHATEVER YOU'RE DOING
TO HELP HIM THROUGH IT.

20:19.250 --> 20:22.219
SURE.

20:25.120 --> 20:26.883
THAN KS.

20:26.890 --> 20:28.289
VERONICA.

20:29.320 --> 20:31.356
I'M GLAD
YOU TWO ARE TOGETHER.

20:31.360 --> 20:34.591
I LIKE WHAT I SEE IN HIM
WHEN HE'S WITH YOU.

20:38.070 --> 20:40.459
THE TALK WITH DAD --
I GUESS THAT MEANS

20:40.470 --> 20:43.837
MY RELATIONSHIP WITH LOGAN
IS OFFICIALLY OFF THE GROUND.

20:43.840 --> 20:45.933
JUST IN TIME FOR
TAD AND CARMEN'S RELATIONSHIP

20:45.940 --> 20:47.999
TO CRASH AND BURN
ON THE BOARDWALK.

20:48.010 --> 20:51.548
[ LOUIS XIV'S "FINDING OUT
TRUE LOVE IS BLIND" PLAYS ]

20:51.550 --> 20:54.246
JEEZ. HOW MUCH VODKA
DID YOU PUT IN THIS THING?

20:54.250 --> 20:55.842
* OH, CHOCOLATE GIRL *

20:55.850 --> 20:58.683
* WELL, YOU'RE LOOKIN' LIKE
SOMETHING I WANT *

20:58.690 --> 21:00.453
* FINDING OUT
TRUE LOVE IS BLIND *

21:00.460 --> 21:01.882
* YOUR LITTLE ASIAN FRIEND *

21:01.890 --> 21:04.688
* WELL, SHE CAN COME
IF SHE WANTS *

21:04.690 --> 21:06.453
* FINDING OUT
TRUE LOVE IS BLIND *

21:06.460 --> 21:08.121
* IT'S THE GIRL IN THE FROWN *

21:08.130 --> 21:10.690
* WITH THE TIGHT PANTS
I REALLY WANT TO SHAKE UP *

21:10.700 --> 21:14.363
* FINDING OUT
TRUE LOVE IS BLIND *

21:17.170 --> 21:18.762
* HEY, CARROT JUICE *

21:18.770 --> 21:20.499
* I WANT TO SQUEEZE YOU
AWAY UNTIL YOU BLEED *

21:20.510 --> 21:22.774
HOW MUCH DO YOU LOVE ME?

21:22.780 --> 21:23.747
HMM?

21:23.750 --> 21:25.479
* AND YOUR VANILLA FRIEND *

21:25.480 --> 21:28.415
* WELL, SHE LOOKS LIKE
SOMETHING I NEED *

21:28.420 --> 21:30.718
* FINDING OUT
TRUE LOVE IS BLIND *

21:30.720 --> 21:33.712
I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT IS
ABOUT YOU, CARMEN,

21:33.720 --> 21:36.848
THAT MAKES ME FEEL
PLUMB LOCO.

21:36.860 --> 21:40.455
DO YOU WANT TO TRY SOMETHING
REALLY CRAZY?

21:40.460 --> 21:42.655
I WANT YOU
TO GO TALK WITH SETH.

21:42.660 --> 21:43.820
* WIND YOU UP *

21:43.830 --> 21:46.321
* AND MAKE YOU CRAWL TO ME *

21:46.330 --> 21:48.537
WHY? DO YOU NEED
FASHION ADVICE?

21:48.540 --> 21:50.531
I HEARD FROM
THAT DRAMA CHICK, GINA,

21:50.540 --> 21:53.304
THAT HE'S GOT
THE BEST "X" IN SCHOOL.

21:53.310 --> 21:54.538
I DON'T KNOW.

21:54.540 --> 21:56.599
I THOUGHT
MAYBE ON PROM NIGHT

21:56.610 --> 22:00.649
YOU'D WANT TO EXPERIMENT WITH ME
AFTER THE DANCE?

22:01.580 --> 22:03.343
THIS IS WHY I LOVE YOU.

22:03.350 --> 22:04.385
MMM.

22:04.390 --> 22:06.642
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

22:06.650 --> 22:09.483
* OH, BROWN GIRL
WITH THE HOT PANTS *

22:09.490 --> 22:10.957
* SHAKING THAT THING
ON THE STREET *

22:10.960 --> 22:12.780
* A FRIDAY NIGHT
TRUE-LOVE DISPLAY *

22:12.790 --> 22:16.351
HEY, SETH.
HEY, WHAT'S UP, MAN?

22:16.360 --> 22:17.725
UM...

22:17.730 --> 22:19.368
* A FRIDAY NIGHT
TRUE-LOVE DISPLAY *

22:19.370 --> 22:20.735
* AND ALL THE TOUGH GIRLS *

22:20.740 --> 22:23.538
* WHO NEVER WANT ME
TO SEE THEM CRY *

22:23.540 --> 22:26.361
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

22:26.370 --> 22:29.806
* AHH AHH AHH AHH AHH AHH *

22:29.810 --> 22:32.973
* A FRIDAY NIGHT
TRUE-LOVE DISPLAY *

22:32.980 --> 22:37.178
ALL WE NEED NOW
IS A SOUNDTRACK.

22:37.180 --> 22:39.319
BE NATURAL.

22:39.320 --> 22:40.514
BE INTIMATE.

22:40.520 --> 22:41.987
AND LET TAD
DO THE TALKING.

22:41.990 --> 22:45.187
HE WILL TIE HIS OWN NOOSE,
GUARANTEED.

22:45.190 --> 22:46.680
[ SPEED-DIALING ]

22:46.690 --> 22:49.250
HOMESTRETCH, GIRLFRIEND.

22:49.260 --> 22:50.488
HEY, TAD.

22:50.500 --> 22:52.559
I HAD SUCH A GREAT TIME
TODAY.

22:52.570 --> 22:54.060
Me too, baby.

22:54.070 --> 22:57.130
I WISH I HAD YOU HERE RIGHT NOW,
THOUGH, IN MY BED.

22:57.140 --> 23:00.678
I CAN'T WAIT UNTIL AFTER PROM
FOR OUR LITTLE, UH...

23:00.680 --> 23:02.329
EROTIC EXPERIMENT.

23:02.340 --> 23:05.673
I HAD NO IDEA YOU'D BE SO INTO
DROPPING "X" TO GET THERE.

23:05.680 --> 23:07.375
Are you kidding me?

23:07.380 --> 23:08.870
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN CURIOUS.

23:08.880 --> 23:12.281
I WAS ALWAYS JUST WORRIED
ABOUT MY PARENTS, YOU KNOW?

23:12.290 --> 23:13.655
Or the naval academy.

23:13.660 --> 23:16.413
They'd kick me out
if they ever found out.

23:16.420 --> 23:18.820
ARE YOU SURE
YOU'RE READY FOR ME?

23:18.830 --> 23:20.457
BIG-TIME.

23:20.460 --> 23:23.429
NIGHTY NIGHT.

23:23.430 --> 23:25.295
SO, HOW WAS THAT?

23:25.300 --> 23:27.689
THAT WAS A LITTLE SCARY.

23:27.700 --> 23:31.704
SO, REMEMBER,
WE'LL MEET FOR LUNCH TOMORROW.

23:31.710 --> 23:34.076
AND DON'T FORGET TAD.

23:36.180 --> 23:37.408
HI, HONEY.

23:37.410 --> 23:39.571
GOOD NEWS.
IT'S CHICKEN KIEV NIGHT.

23:39.580 --> 23:41.445
AND THIS TIME --
NEXT TIME.

23:41.450 --> 23:43.008
I GOT TO RUN.

23:43.020 --> 23:45.147
THE MYSTERY BAG?
ON A TUESDAY?

23:45.150 --> 23:48.085
MY OWN DAD HAS LOST
TOTAL LIBIDINAL CONTROL.

23:48.090 --> 23:51.651
ARE YOU SURE? THERE'S IMPORTANT
TEEN ISSUES WE COULD DISCUSS.

23:51.660 --> 23:54.754
OH, THE CAR DUNCAN BOUGHT --
I JUST GOT A TIP.

23:54.760 --> 23:57.251
IT WAS SPOTTED
OUTSIDE TIJUANA.

23:57.260 --> 23:59.490
YALE, BABY!

24:06.970 --> 24:09.609
HE'S IN ROOM WHAT?
QU NMERO?

24:09.610 --> 24:10.907
OCHO.

24:10.910 --> 24:12.446
GRACIAS.

24:14.580 --> 24:17.708
[ ROOSTER CROWS ]

24:19.520 --> 24:21.715
[ Mexican accent ]
ROOM SERVICE!

24:21.720 --> 24:24.052
[ Normal voice ] IT'S ABOUT TIME
YOU CAME HOME, DUNC--

24:24.060 --> 24:24.856
[ GASPS ]

24:24.860 --> 24:26.680
DUNCAN, WHAT ARE YOU --

24:27.960 --> 24:31.760
THE, UH, CAR OUT FRONT --
THE IMPALA?

24:31.770 --> 24:33.931
THE IMPALA, S.

24:33.940 --> 24:35.339
IT'S YOURS?

24:35.340 --> 24:36.693
IT'S A BUST, SWEETIE.

24:36.700 --> 24:38.804
THE CAR WAS ABANDONED
OUTSIDE THE BUS STATION,

24:38.810 --> 24:40.129
A CASE OF BEER IN THE SEAT,

24:40.140 --> 24:42.608
AND A SIGN IN SPANISH
SAYING "FREE CAR."

24:42.610 --> 24:44.077
A DECOY.

24:44.080 --> 24:46.605
MAYBE DUNCAN'S SMARTER
THAN I WAS GIVING HIM CREDIT.

24:46.610 --> 24:48.874
WELL,
HE DID ACE HIS P.S.A.T.s.

24:48.880 --> 24:51.144
SO, I'LL SEE YOU AT HOME
FOR DINNER?

24:51.150 --> 24:53.345
Rain check, honey.
Alicia and I...

24:53.350 --> 24:54.658
ARE GOING OUT. RIGHT.

24:54.660 --> 24:57.686
WELL, I'LL SEE YOU
WHEN I SEE YOU.

24:57.690 --> 24:59.157
ARE YOU BUSY?

24:59.160 --> 25:02.027
STILL WORKING
ON THAT PASSPORT THING.

25:02.030 --> 25:03.019
CHECK IT OUT.

25:03.030 --> 25:05.396
I JUST FOUND
MR. HEINRICH'S POSTING

25:05.400 --> 25:07.630
ON THE NEPTUNE
"SWINGLES" SITE.

25:07.640 --> 25:09.835
OOH, LARRY.

25:09.840 --> 25:11.933
* BOW CHICKA BOW-BOW *

25:11.940 --> 25:13.931
[ LAUGHS ]
WHAT DO YOU NEED?

25:13.940 --> 25:15.908
UH, ALONG
THOSE SAME LINES,

25:15.910 --> 25:19.277
HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE TO CREATE
A HIGHLY INCRIMINATING,

25:19.280 --> 25:22.477
THOROUGHLY LIBELOUS,
SEXUALLY EXPLICIT WEBSITE?

25:22.480 --> 25:26.280
UHH, 45 MINUTES,
GIVE OR TAKE.

25:26.290 --> 25:29.054
I'LL GET STARTED
AS SOON AS I'M DONE READING

25:29.060 --> 25:31.927
ABOUT HOW
MR. HEINRICH'S INTERESTS

25:31.930 --> 25:33.727
INCLUDE HORSEBACK RIDING
ON THE BEACH,

25:33.730 --> 25:36.119
HOT-TUBBING
WITH SPECIAL FRIENDS, AND...

25:36.130 --> 25:37.222
"sensual charades."

25:37.230 --> 25:38.788
OH, THAN KS, MAC.

25:38.800 --> 25:41.268
THAT'S A MENTAL IMAGE
I'LL CARRY WITH ME TO THE GRAVE.

25:41.270 --> 25:43.158
IS THAT MY MATH TEACHER?

25:43.170 --> 25:44.330
HERE'S THE AMMO.

25:44.340 --> 25:47.673
SETH HERE WILL HELP YOU
WITH THE REST.

25:54.050 --> 25:55.540
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

25:55.550 --> 25:58.815
I'M HERE
TO OFFER YOU A DEAL.

25:58.820 --> 26:00.242
I WANT MY CELLPHONE BACK.

26:00.250 --> 26:01.808
OF COURSE.

26:04.860 --> 26:06.327
NEXT ORDER OF BUSINESS.

26:06.330 --> 26:08.821
YOU AND CARMEN ARE BROKEN UP,
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY.

26:08.830 --> 26:11.298
WHAT ABOUT YESTERDAY?

26:11.300 --> 26:12.767
THE BOARDWALK?

26:12.770 --> 26:14.032
MY TATTOO?

26:14.040 --> 26:15.689
IT'S CALLED "PRETENDING."

26:15.700 --> 26:17.031
I DON'T LOVE YOU ANYMORE.

26:17.040 --> 26:19.167
AND YOU CAN'T
BLACKMAIL ME INTO IT.

26:19.170 --> 26:22.537
CARMEN, I SWEAR,
I NEVER WANTED TO HURT YOU.

26:22.540 --> 26:24.849
YOU MADE ME DO IT.

26:24.850 --> 26:26.545
IF YOU MAKE ME
DO IT AGAIN --

26:26.550 --> 26:28.871
SHE'LL HURT YOU WORSE.

26:28.880 --> 26:31.087
* OUR MOTHERS AND FATHERS *

26:31.090 --> 26:32.341
WHAT'S THAT?

26:32.350 --> 26:34.716
SETH'S WEB PAGE,
DEVOTED TO YOUR FORBIDDEN LOVE.

26:34.720 --> 26:37.985
BEAUTIFUL SONG
YOU WROTE FOR HIM.

26:37.990 --> 26:40.959
* SO WE FOLLOW THE RAINBOW *

26:40.960 --> 26:43.690
* TO AN UNCHARTED LAND *

26:43.700 --> 26:45.918
IT'S A BUNCH OF CRAP.

26:45.930 --> 26:48.160
YOU GUYS JUST FAKED THAT
WITH PHOTOSHOP.

26:48.170 --> 26:50.331
NO ONE'S
GONNA BELIEVE THIS.

26:50.340 --> 26:51.568
AH?

26:51.570 --> 26:52.969
OOH...

26:53.910 --> 26:55.229
Seth: HEY, TAD.

26:55.240 --> 26:57.003
Tad: I CAN'T WAIT
UNTIL AFTER PROM

26:57.010 --> 26:59.103
FOR OUR LITTLE, UH,
EROTIC EXPERIMENT.

26:59.110 --> 27:01.977
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME
YOU WERE INTO GUYS?

27:01.980 --> 27:04.540
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN CURIOUS.

27:04.550 --> 27:07.917
I WAS ALWAYS JUST WORRIED
ABOUT MY PARENTS, YOU KNOW?

27:07.920 --> 27:09.353
OR THE NAVAL ACADEMY.

27:09.360 --> 27:12.579
THEY'D KICK ME OUT
IF THEY EVER FOUND OUT.

27:12.590 --> 27:14.296
SEEN ENOUGH?

27:14.300 --> 27:17.258
WHATEVER. WHO CARES ABOUT WHAT
THIS SCHOOL THINKS ABOUT ME?

27:17.260 --> 27:18.466
I'M GONE IN A MONTH.

27:18.470 --> 27:21.860
ACTUALLY, I WAS ABLE
TO GET THE E-MAIL ADDRESSES

27:21.870 --> 27:23.531
OF EVERY PLEBE
AT ANNAPOLIS.

27:23.540 --> 27:26.407
ONE PRESS OF A BUTTON,
AND EACH OF YOUR NEW CLASSMATES

27:26.410 --> 27:29.129
WILL HAVE THE LINK
TO THIS VERY SPECIAL WEBSITE.

27:29.140 --> 27:32.246
THE NAW'S GOT THAT
"DON'T ASK, DON'T TELL" THING.

27:32.250 --> 27:34.673
IF WE TELL,
THEY'RE GONNA ASK.

27:34.680 --> 27:36.716
MUTUALLY ASSURED
DESTRUCTION.

27:36.720 --> 27:38.688
THINK HARD, TAD.

27:40.920 --> 27:42.319
LOOK, CARMEN --

27:42.320 --> 27:45.426
I DON'T EVER WANT
TO SPEAK TO YOU AGAIN.

27:46.860 --> 27:48.748
Man: LET'S GO.

27:48.760 --> 27:50.921
COME ON.

27:50.930 --> 27:53.069
AH, MASS TRANSIT.

27:53.070 --> 27:56.062
WHY TAKE THE BUS WHEN YOU CAN
DRIVE YOUR OWN RUST BUCKET?

27:56.070 --> 27:58.834
I HAD MY DAD'S DRIVER
PICK IT UP.

27:58.840 --> 28:01.536
FULL OF FRESH STOLEN PARTS,
READY TO GO.

28:01.540 --> 28:03.201
[ KEYS JINGLE ]

28:07.250 --> 28:08.512
WOW.

28:08.520 --> 28:11.785
I'LL TRY TO KEEP THIS GESTURE
IN MIND THIS WEEKEND,

28:11.790 --> 28:13.439
WHEN YOU AND DICK
AND THE BEAVER

28:13.450 --> 28:16.749
ARE OFF GETTING BLASTED
AND SCAMMING CHEERLEADERS.

28:16.760 --> 28:18.182
YEAH. YEAH.

28:18.190 --> 28:20.954
ACTUALLY, I HAD TO TELL DICK
I'M NOT AVAILABLE,

28:20.960 --> 28:22.427
BECAUSE I HAVE
OTHER PLANS.

28:22.430 --> 28:25.297
THERE ARE CHEERLEADERS
WITH LOW SELF-ESTEEM

28:25.300 --> 28:26.528
AVAILABLE DOM ESTICALLY?

28:26.530 --> 28:29.863
ARE YOU FREE FRIDAY?
MAYBE WE COULD GO OUT.

28:31.010 --> 28:33.001
HERE? IN NEPTUNE?

28:33.010 --> 28:35.808
WHAT ABOUT
OUR LITTLE SECRET?

28:35.810 --> 28:37.368
WELL...

28:37.380 --> 28:40.406
I THOUGHT WE'D TRY A
PRACTICE RUN ON CATALINA ISLAND.

28:41.380 --> 28:43.814
WHAT DO YOU THINK
ABOUT SKIPPING SCHOOL FRIDAY

28:43.820 --> 28:44.980
FOR A RIDE ON DAD'S BOAT?

28:44.990 --> 28:47.311
DINNER AND A MOVIE?

28:47.320 --> 28:48.958
I'LL PENCIL YOU IN.

28:48.960 --> 28:52.555
SO IT'S, UH --
WHAT IS THE WORD?

28:52.560 --> 28:53.959
A DATE?

28:53.960 --> 28:56.497
NICE OF YOUR DAD
TO LET US USE HIS BOAT.

28:56.500 --> 28:58.764
YEAH, YEAH.
I THINK HE ACTUALLY LIKES YOU.

28:58.770 --> 29:02.365
WHEN HE HEARD THAT STUFF
ABOUT YOUR PARENTS, I THINK --

29:02.370 --> 29:03.860
WHAT? WHAT STUFF?

29:03.870 --> 29:05.701
LOGAN!

29:05.710 --> 29:07.302
WHAT THE HELL, MAN?

29:07.310 --> 29:10.279
JUST, UH, THERE WAS SOMETHING
IN THE PAPER, HE SAID.

29:10.280 --> 29:13.909
SO 10:00ish,
ALBACORE CLUB, SLIP 5.

29:28.530 --> 29:30.691
OH, MY GOD.

29:30.700 --> 29:32.292
"SEEKING LIANNE MARS.

29:32.300 --> 29:34.188
"PLEASE CONTACT THIS NUMBER
IMMEDIATELY.

29:34.200 --> 29:37.237
LEGAL PROCEEDINGS HAVE BEGUN
IN YOUR NAME."

29:39.640 --> 29:41.107
I KNOW
WHAT "ENTRAPMENT" IS.

29:41.110 --> 29:43.908
ACTUALLY, LORETTA,
I DON'T THINK YOU DO.

29:43.910 --> 29:45.798
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

29:45.810 --> 29:47.448
YEAH, IT'S CLIFF.

29:47.450 --> 29:50.044
YES, I'M ALWAYS AVAILABLE
FOR YOU.

29:50.050 --> 29:51.642
THIS IS ENTRAPMENT.

29:51.650 --> 29:54.312
IF THAT'S TAMARA, TELL THAT
BITCH SHE CAN BEG ALL SHE WANTS.

29:54.320 --> 29:55.582
I'M TESTIFYING.

29:55.590 --> 29:57.888
MS. CANCUN, PLEASE.
YOU'RE NOT HELPING YOURSELF.

29:57.890 --> 29:59.448
Veronica,
what do you need?

29:59.460 --> 30:01.997
WHY WOULD SOMEONE PLACE
A NOTICE OF LEGAL PROCEEDINGS

30:02.000 --> 30:03.399
IN THE CLASSIFIED SECTION?

30:03.400 --> 30:05.561
IT COULD BE ANYTHING.
CAN YOU BE MORE SPECIFIC?

30:05.570 --> 30:09.461
LIKE, SAY, A MAN SEEKING
THE WHEREABOUTS OF A WOMAN.

30:09.470 --> 30:13.338
IT COULD BE CHILD SUPPORT,
A CIVIL SUIT, DIVORCE.

30:13.340 --> 30:15.604
YOU JUST SIGN RIGHT HERE,
DEAR.

30:15.610 --> 30:17.430
DIVORCE?

30:19.110 --> 30:20.668
"SCREW YOU, PIG."

30:20.680 --> 30:23.444
NICE. OKAY,
LIKE A BIG GIRL NOW.

30:23.450 --> 30:27.216
CALIFORNIA LAW, YOU HAVE TO RUN
A NOTICE FOR SEVEN DAYS

30:27.220 --> 30:30.781
BEFORE YOU CAN FILE FOR DIVORCE
ON GROUNDS OF ABANDONMENT --

30:30.790 --> 30:32.155
[ SIGHS ]

30:32.160 --> 30:35.425
I GOT TO RUN, "V."

30:42.840 --> 30:47.903
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6.

30:47.910 --> 30:51.277
ONE MORE DAY BEFORE
WHATEVER IS HAPPENING HAPPENS.

30:51.280 --> 30:53.544
AND LIANNE MARS RETURNS
CLEAN AND SOBER

30:53.550 --> 30:57.270
TO A HOME THAT
NO LONGER HAS A PLACE FOR HER.

30:58.890 --> 31:00.346
Classifieds.

31:00.350 --> 31:02.079
HI, THIS IS VERONICA,
KEITH MARS' ASSISTANT,

31:02.090 --> 31:04.251
WHO PLACED A LEGAL NOTICE
IN YOUR PAPER

31:04.260 --> 31:05.557
AT THE START OF THE WEEK.

31:05.560 --> 31:07.448
MR. MARS' LEGAL SITUATION
HAS CHANGED.

31:07.460 --> 31:09.519
HE WON'T BE NEEDING
TO RUN THE AD TOMORROW.

31:09.530 --> 31:12.260
Good thing you called.
We're an hour from deadline.

31:12.270 --> 31:14.397
If you can just confirm
Mr. Mars' address,

31:14.400 --> 31:17.130
credit information,
and Mr. Mars' account password,

31:17.140 --> 31:19.005
we'll take care of that
for you.

31:19.010 --> 31:20.705
ACCOUNT PASSWORD.

31:20.710 --> 31:22.530
OF COURSE -- THEY HAVE TO HAVE
SOMETHING SENSIBLE,

31:22.540 --> 31:24.599
LIKE A PASSWORD,
TO PREVENT PEOPLE LIKE ME

31:24.610 --> 31:26.771
FROM DOING
WHAT I'M TRYING TO DO.

31:26.780 --> 31:28.509
Miss?

31:36.690 --> 31:38.555
I MIGHT FEEL
A LITTLE UNCOMFORTABLE

31:38.560 --> 31:40.380
ABOUT TRACKING
MY DAD'S CELLPHONE

31:40.390 --> 31:43.496
IF HE HADN'T
DONE IT TO ME FIRST.

31:43.500 --> 31:45.695
A HOTEL. GREAT.

31:45.700 --> 31:49.295
SUDDENLY I'M FEELING
A LITTLE QUEASY.

31:49.300 --> 31:51.803
WE HAVE NO ONE UNDER "MARS"
OR "FENNEL" STAYING WITH US.

31:51.810 --> 31:54.233
AND TRYING
ALL THE MR. AND MRS. SMITHS

31:54.240 --> 31:55.776
IS OUT OF THE QUESTION?

31:55.780 --> 31:57.668
THANKS ANYWAY.

31:57.680 --> 32:02.117
* IN TIME,
THE ROCKIES MAY CRUMBLE *

32:02.120 --> 32:04.611
* GIBRALTAR MAY TUMBLE *

32:04.620 --> 32:07.441
* THEY'RE ONLY MADE OF CLAY *

32:07.450 --> 32:15.926
* BUT OUR LOVE
IS HERE TO STAY *

32:15.930 --> 32:17.056
TAKE IT, ELLA.

32:17.060 --> 32:21.269
* IT'S VERY CLEAR *

32:21.270 --> 32:26.799
* OUR LOVE IS HERE
TO STAY *

32:26.810 --> 32:31.247
OKAY, DAD, I GET IT --
YOU'RE HAPPY.

32:31.250 --> 32:34.413
* BUT EVER AND A DAY *

32:34.420 --> 32:37.344
GOOD MORNING.

32:37.350 --> 32:40.444
IT IS GOOD, ISN'T IT?

32:40.450 --> 32:42.054
HEY, CARMEN.

32:42.960 --> 32:44.188
HI.

32:44.190 --> 32:45.919
I WAS WONDERING
IF YOU'RE HUNGRY.

32:45.930 --> 32:47.329
NO.

32:47.330 --> 32:49.958
I THOUGHT YOU MIGHT WANT
TO SUCK MY POPSICLE.

32:49.960 --> 32:51.291
[ LAUGHTER ]

32:51.300 --> 32:54.098
TAD PRESSED THE BUTTON.

32:58.540 --> 33:00.098
Carmen:
WHAT IF SOMEBODY CATCHES US?

33:00.110 --> 33:01.577
Tad:
NO ONE IS GONNA CATCH US.

33:01.580 --> 33:04.299
NO WAY.
MAN, YOU REALLY DID MISS OUT.

33:04.310 --> 33:05.971
THAT CARMEN IS FREAKY!

33:05.980 --> 33:07.504
[ LAUGHS ]

33:07.510 --> 33:10.638
HEY, WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU, MAN?
WHERE'D THIS COME FROM?

33:13.820 --> 33:16.118
[ CRYING ]

33:19.030 --> 33:20.122
HEY.

33:20.130 --> 33:21.529
[ SNIFFLES ]

33:21.530 --> 33:24.226
I SAW YOUR CAR
WAS STILL IN THE LOT.

33:24.230 --> 33:27.267
I WAS WAITING
FOR THE REST OF SCHOOL TO LEAVE

33:27.270 --> 33:28.692
SO THAT I COULD SNEAK HOME

33:28.700 --> 33:31.806
WITHOUT BEING ASSAILED
WITH ANY FROZEN DESSERTS.

33:31.810 --> 33:34.677
ALTHOUGH I'M SURE MY PARENTS
HAVE SEEN THE VIDEO,

33:34.680 --> 33:38.548
SO I'M NOT EXACTLY SURE
WHERE I'M PLANNING TO HIDE.

33:38.550 --> 33:41.576
SOMEWHERE
THEY DON'T HAVE COMPUTERS.

33:41.580 --> 33:43.741
I CAN'T BELIEVE
HE DID IT.

33:43.750 --> 33:45.786
IMAGINE MY SURPRISE.

33:47.350 --> 33:49.409
YOU KNOW WHAT?
SCREW IT.

33:49.420 --> 33:53.550
I'M STILL GLAD
I DUMPED THAT IDIOT LOSER...

33:53.560 --> 33:55.118
CRAPFACE.

33:55.130 --> 33:56.495
[ LAUGHS ]

33:56.500 --> 33:59.367
I'D RATHER THE WHOLE WORLD
THINK I'M TRASHY

33:59.370 --> 34:02.635
THAN HAVE A GUY LIKE TAD
THINK HE CAN PUSH ME AROUND.

34:02.640 --> 34:04.665
AT LEAST NOW IT'S OVER.

34:04.670 --> 34:08.174
NO MORE WAITING
FOR THE BOMB TO DROP.

34:08.180 --> 34:09.329
THAT'S RIGHT.

34:09.340 --> 34:11.877
NO MORE WAITING.

34:11.880 --> 34:14.246
TIME TO STRIKE BACK.

34:16.180 --> 34:18.239
MUTUALLY ASSURED
DESTRUCTION.

34:18.250 --> 34:20.787
THE HONOR IS YOURS.

34:37.070 --> 34:38.560
THANKS ANYWAY.

34:38.570 --> 34:41.835
YOU CAN'T LET HIM
GET AWAY WITH IT.

34:41.840 --> 34:46.777
TEARING TAD DOWN
ISN'T GONNA MAKE ME FEEL BETTER.

34:47.650 --> 34:49.777
CARMEN,
I CAN'T STRESS ENOUGH --

34:49.780 --> 34:51.077
SORRY, VERONICA.

34:51.080 --> 34:54.379
I GUESS REVENGE
JUST ISN'T MY THING.

34:57.490 --> 34:58.821
[YOUNG MEN LAUGHING ]

34:58.830 --> 35:00.650
Carmen:
WHAT IF SOMEBODY CATCHES US?

35:00.660 --> 35:04.164
Tad:
NO ONE IS GONNA CATCH US.

35:04.170 --> 35:07.059
MMM.

35:07.070 --> 35:08.560
MMM.

35:08.570 --> 35:09.366
MMM!

35:09.370 --> 35:10.792
IT'S ALL FUN AND GAMES

35:10.800 --> 35:13.234
UNTIL ONE OF YOU GETS
MY FOOT UP YOUR ASS.

35:13.240 --> 35:17.700
[ LAUGHING ]

35:17.710 --> 35:18.972
MMM.

35:18.980 --> 35:21.141
MMM.

35:24.590 --> 35:25.909
OH, MY GOD.

35:25.920 --> 35:28.957
I REMEMBER THOSE STARS
AND CHINESE LAMPS.

35:28.960 --> 35:32.555
THEY'RE ABOUT THE ONLY THINGS
I REMEMBER FROM THAT NIGHT.

35:32.560 --> 35:38.055
A YEAR AND A HALF AGO,
SHELLY POMEROY HAD A PARTY.

35:38.060 --> 35:39.493
[ LAUGHTER ]

35:44.510 --> 35:46.330
COULD IT BE THAT THE NIGHT

35:46.340 --> 35:49.434
CARMEN GAVE A SEX SHOW IN THE
HOT TUB THAT SHE CAN'T REMEMBER

35:49.440 --> 35:50.976
WAS THE SAME NIGHT

35:50.980 --> 35:54.211
I WAS DRUGGED AND RAPED
IN A GUEST BEDROOM?

35:54.220 --> 35:56.142
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

35:58.120 --> 36:00.088
I KNOW
I SHOULD HAVE TOLD YOU.

36:00.090 --> 36:02.786
NO. YOUR LIFE
IS YOUR BUSINESS.

36:02.790 --> 36:05.918
I JUST FELT,
AFTER A YEAR OF NOT KNOWING,

36:05.930 --> 36:07.557
I WANTED OPTIONS.

36:07.560 --> 36:09.858
IF I EVER
DECIDED TO MOVE ON,

36:09.860 --> 36:12.897
SERVING NOTICE
IS JUST A FIRST STEP.

36:12.900 --> 36:16.165
AND IF I THINK
I MIGHT TAKE ANOTHER...

36:19.810 --> 36:21.903
NO MORE SURPRISES.
I PROMISE.

36:21.910 --> 36:25.175
I JUST WANT YOU
TO BE HAPPY, DAD.

36:25.180 --> 36:29.310
AND I REALIZE
THAT MAY INVOLVE...SURPRISES.

36:33.850 --> 36:34.919
[ SIGHS ]

36:34.920 --> 36:37.616
ROBERTO NALBAN DION.

36:37.620 --> 36:40.259
WHO'S ROBERTO NALBANDION?

36:40.260 --> 36:41.796
I HAVE NO IDEA.

36:41.800 --> 36:43.927
OKAY, FORGIVE ME IF,
AS OF YET, I'M UNIMPRESSED.

36:43.930 --> 36:47.263
I DON'T KNOW WHO HE IS,
BUT I DO KNOW SOMEONE PURCHASED

36:47.270 --> 36:49.363
HIS ARGENTINEAN PASSPORT
OFF OF eBAY

36:49.370 --> 36:52.259
AND HAD IT SHIPPED
TO THE AIRPORT MARRIOTT.

36:52.270 --> 36:53.601
DAD, THIS IS MAC.

36:53.610 --> 36:55.237
SHE KNOWS HER WAY
AROUND A COMPUTER.

36:55.240 --> 36:56.832
MAC, MY DAD.

36:56.840 --> 36:58.740
SO. . .ARGENTINA.

36:58.750 --> 37:01.412
[ Spanish accent ]
ROBERTO NALBANDION.

37:01.420 --> 37:03.877
THAT'S GREAT.

37:03.880 --> 37:05.245
[ HUMMING TANGO MUSIC ]

37:05.250 --> 37:06.649
[ LAUGHS ]

37:06.650 --> 37:10.518
SO...
THE BOUNTY ON DUNCAN.

37:10.520 --> 37:12.226
WHAT'S MY SHARE?

37:12.230 --> 37:14.050
8?

37:14.060 --> 37:15.049
10?

37:15.060 --> 37:16.220
$10.

37:16.230 --> 37:17.959
BUT YOU DRIVE
A HARD BARGAIN.

37:17.960 --> 37:19.825
I MEANT PERCENT.

37:19.830 --> 37:21.058
YOU'LL GET YOUR CUT.

37:21.070 --> 37:23.538
NEW QUESTION -- IS THERE
ANY WAY TO FIGURE OUT

37:23.540 --> 37:26.407
WHEN A VIDEO WAS RECORDED
ON SOMEONE'S CELLPHONE?

37:26.410 --> 37:29.629
SURE. EVERY MPEG
HAS AN EMBEDDED TIME STAMP.

37:29.640 --> 37:30.937
OKAY.

37:30.940 --> 37:33.443
CARMEN'S VIDEO.
I'VE GOT IT UP ON THE SCREEN.

37:33.450 --> 37:35.645
SURE. NO PROBLEM.

37:40.090 --> 37:42.558
IT SAYS THE IMAGE
WAS CAPTURED

37:42.560 --> 37:45.882
AT 3:23 A.M.,
DECEMBER 7, 2003.

37:45.890 --> 37:50.589
I CAN'T BELIEVE
THAT BUTTHEAD SENT IT OUT.

37:52.200 --> 37:55.363
WHAT? DOES THAT DATE
MEAN SOMETHING?

37:55.370 --> 37:57.099
NOTHING.

37:57.100 --> 38:00.467
ONLY THAT CARMEN AND I
DON'T REMEMBER THE SAME NIGHT.

38:00.470 --> 38:02.233
NO, I JUST HAVE A MEETING.

38:02.240 --> 38:06.040
BUT YOU HAVE UNTIL 5:30
TO DECIDE -- CHICKEN OR FISH.

38:08.480 --> 38:12.314
BYE, KEITH.
[ LAUGHS ]

38:13.750 --> 38:17.311
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME,
MISTER...?

38:17.320 --> 38:18.582
CLARENCE WIEDMAN.

38:18.590 --> 38:20.751
I'M WITH SECURITY HERE,
MS. FENNEL.

38:20.760 --> 38:23.320
I WANTED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT KEITH MARS.

38:23.330 --> 38:24.729
WHAT?

38:24.730 --> 38:26.618
I KNOW
YOU'VE BEEN SEEING MR. MARS

38:26.630 --> 38:28.029
FOR THE PAST COUPLE MONTHS.

38:28.030 --> 38:29.668
WHAT YOU MAY NOT KNOW --

38:29.670 --> 38:32.059
HE IS MAN
WITH A KNOWN GRUDGE

38:32.070 --> 38:35.779
AGAINST THE KANE FAMILY
AND THIS COMPANY.

38:35.780 --> 38:38.032
I'M GONNA HAVE TO ASK YOU
TO STOP SEEING HIM

38:38.040 --> 38:41.009
IF YOU WANT TO AVOID
PROBLEMS WITH YOUR JOB.

38:42.180 --> 38:46.389
LOOK, MR. WEED,
OR WHATEVER YOUR NAME IS,

38:46.390 --> 38:48.381
I HAVE BEEN
A PERFECT EMPLOYEE

38:48.390 --> 38:50.255
SINCE I STEPPED THROUGH
THAT DOOR.

38:50.260 --> 38:52.057
AND I HAVE
NEVER DONE ANYTHING

38:52.060 --> 38:55.154
TO RAISE QUESTIONS
AS TO MY DEDICATION TO MY JOB.

38:55.160 --> 38:57.048
THE IDEA
THAT YOU CAN TELL ME

38:57.060 --> 39:00.518
WHAT I CAN AND CAN'T DO
WITH MY PERSONAL LIFE...

39:00.530 --> 39:02.031
WELL, CLARENCE --

39:02.040 --> 39:03.439
MS. FENNEL...

39:03.440 --> 39:05.499
YOU KNOW WHAT THIS IS?

39:08.880 --> 39:12.247
THIS IS AN ELECTRONIC
EAVESDROPPING DEVICE.

39:12.250 --> 39:13.842
A BUG.

39:13.850 --> 39:15.738
I FOUND IT
IN THAT HOUSE PLANT,

39:15.750 --> 39:18.947
WHICH HAS BEEN IN MY OFFICE
FOR THE LAST SEVERAL WEEKS.

39:18.950 --> 39:21.612
YOU KNOW
WHO DELIVERED IT?

39:23.590 --> 39:26.457
YOUR SON, WALLACE.

39:28.460 --> 39:29.996
LIKE I SAID...

39:30.000 --> 39:31.922
YOU REALLY MIGHT WANT
TO RECONSIDER

39:31.930 --> 39:34.398
YOUR RELATIONSHIP
WITH MR. MARS.

39:36.100 --> 39:38.739
AN HOUR EARLY TO SCHOOL
IS PRETTY BROWN-NOSEY.

39:38.740 --> 39:40.139
BUT EVEN AT NEPTUNE,

39:40.140 --> 39:41.869
YACHTING IS NOT
A RECOGNIZED EXCUSE

39:41.880 --> 39:44.405
FOR A LATE ENGLISH REPORT.

39:45.210 --> 39:47.872
HOW'S IT HANGING,
TAD?

39:47.880 --> 39:49.871
LET ME GUESS.

39:49.880 --> 39:51.643
UNCOMFORTABLE?

39:53.150 --> 39:56.017
I GUESS YOU AND CARMEN
GOT THOSE BIKERS TO PUT ME HERE.

39:56.020 --> 39:59.080
I HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH PUTTING YOU UP HERE.

39:59.090 --> 40:03.720
BUT I MIGHT BE CONVINCED
TO HELP YOU GET DOWN.

40:03.730 --> 40:05.698
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME,
BITCH?

40:05.700 --> 40:07.964
YOU DESTROYED MY LIFE.

40:07.970 --> 40:10.131
YOU TOOK AWAY THE ONLY PERSON
THAT I EVER LOVED.

40:10.140 --> 40:13.303
I DON'T RECALL FORCING YOU
TO SEND THAT VIDEO.

40:13.310 --> 40:14.868
NO, SHE DID.
SHE LEFT ME.

40:14.880 --> 40:17.474
AND WHAT GOOD
DID SENDING IT DO?

40:17.480 --> 40:20.404
WHO'S GONNA WANT
TO TOUCH HER NOW?

40:20.410 --> 40:23.140
IF I CAN'T HAVE HER,
NO ONE CAN.

40:23.150 --> 40:26.039
YOU ARE SO LUCKY
SHE HAS A BETTER SOUL THAN I DO,

40:26.050 --> 40:28.689
BECAUSE I WOULD HAVE
TAKEN YOU DOWN WITH ME.

40:28.690 --> 40:32.956
SO, ARE YOU GONNA CUT ME DOWN
IF I APOLOGIZE? IS THAT IT?

40:32.960 --> 40:34.382
NOPE.

40:34.390 --> 40:38.565
I JUST WANT A SIMPLE ANSWER
TO A SIMPLE QUESTION.

40:38.570 --> 40:39.969
WHO GAVE YOU
THE ROHYPNOL

40:39.970 --> 40:42.438
THE NIGHT
OF SHELLY POMEROY'S PARTY?

